{"tid":882082,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"牛津研究：中年處男　患攝護腺癌機率少","createTime":"2018-10-30T02:25:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-30T02:56:23.000Z","uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"76a12de3a3c9b220a51339e1620b0401e7086796","tid":882082,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T02:25:35.000Z","msg":"英國牛津大學一項研究發現，如果中年男子仍是處男，患攝護腺癌機會比性生活活躍的男士少47%。<br />\n <br />\n英國《太陽報》前天報導，研究人員調查了22萬名年齡介於40至69歲的男子，發現中年處男患攝護腺癌，比性生活活躍男士的機率，少了47%。<br />\n <br />\n攝護腺癌是英國男士「頭號敵人」，平均每8名男士便有1人患病。<br />\n <br />\n負責研究的蒂姆基（Tim Key）教授表示，「（患者）透過性行為感染，增加患攝護腺癌風險，這個可能性存在。」蒂姆教授指另一個可能性與低水平睪丸酮水平有關，因為睪丸酮水平低便能避免患前列腺患癌，「因為（睪丸酮）是性荷爾蒙，這或許可以解為何這些男士對性興趣不大。」"},{"pid":"76294ceaede5d0165f0ca08b6ec5b6f37bf5c885","tid":882082,"uid":85461,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T02:27:00.000Z","msg":"英國研究"},{"pid":"24e4261408af3c7a684fabd2a7256844a79517e3","tid":882082,"uid":37733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T02:31:40.000Z","msg":"去到中年都仲係處男<br />\n要咁長命做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aac5430b6f6b869a7ec5ad3be4b6a2b9b89b06bc","tid":882082,"uid":37942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"24e4261408af3c7a684fabd2a7256844a79517e3","tid":882082,"uid":37733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T02:31:40.000Z","msg":"去到中年都仲係處男<br />\n要咁長命做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T02:51:20.000Z","msg":"冇所謂啦，大把野玩"},{"pid":"9fbf47f548a60fcbbf5f72f907a85bd59d2083be","tid":882082,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"24e4261408af3c7a684fabd2a7256844a79517e3","tid":882082,"uid":37733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T02:31:40.000Z","msg":"去到中年都仲係處男<br />\n要咁長命做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T02:52:26.000Z","msg":"淨係識扑野<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42a4d2daf583766d36eafabb29b311832d2d91cb","tid":882082,"uid":67500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T02:56:23.000Z","msg":"身體識分打飛機定係扑野既咩??  不就是射精嗎?"}]}